com.esri.mo2.data.odb
Class ObjectDataStore

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.mo2.data.odb.ObjectDataStore
Direct Known Subclasses:
CachedObjectDataStore
public class ObjectDataStore
extends Object

This object data is based on a disk based persistent heap and a memory based object identifier hash table. Given any object that can be serialized and an associated object id, this class creates an object database without multi-user considerations and without a frontend cache.
